org.apache.storm.trident.spout

インタフェース ITridentDataSource

  • すべてのスーパーインタフェース:
    Serializable
    既知のサブインタフェースのリスト:
    IBatchSpout, ICommitterTridentSpout<X>, IOpaquePartitionedTridentSpout<Partitions,Partition,M>, IPartitionedTridentSpout<Partitions,Partition,T>, ITridentSpout<T>
    既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    BatchSpoutExecutor, FeederBatchSpout, FeederCommitterBatchSpout, FixedBatchSpout, OpaquePartitionedTridentSpoutExecutor, OpaqueTridentEventHubSpout, OpaqueTridentKafkaSpout, PartitionedTridentSpoutExecutor, RandomNumberGeneratorSpout, RichSpoutBatchExecutor, TransactionalTridentEventHubSpout, TransactionalTridentKafkaSpout

    public interface ITridentDataSource
extends Serializable

    ITridentDataSource marks all spouts that provide data into Trident.
